</div>Hopefully Andre isn't the blacksmith? I gave him that thing for making weapons divine that you get from the dead blacksmith in the tower and he seemed to just snatch it for his own, so I was forced to murder him thinking he'd drop it. Unfortunately he didn't drop it, but he dropped the 20,000 soul key to the locked door in the garden so a wash there. He now sits peacefully by the local fire. I had found that other smith in the ruins so found him to be expendable. Pretty funny when you attack him btw. He knows karate haha.<br />
