			<div class="postrow">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Dark Souls: My (new) All-Time Favorite Game.
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1833595">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							PS about the Asylum and Laurentius-- I'll leave you to explore on your own unless you really want spoilers.  Laurentius can be rescued in an area you've probably been through (he's not hard to find but he's not hard to miss either).  Just remember to roll into the barrels...<br />
<br />
You can get back to the asylum from Firelink in a manner similar to the way you left it.
