				<div class="message">I'll probably continue focusing on STR/DEX for the short term since I have a weapon I can use and don't care to cheat and read spoilers to find the others. Also, if the ghosts drop a simple cursed weapon I can just use it. I found the vendor who sells curses. On curses, how do you know if the curse has taken hold? My stats didn't seem to change.</div>
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>There will be a white particle effect on your character, and you won't be able to use another Transient Curse (or any other personal buff, like Power Within, Iron Flesh, or Green Blossom) until the curse timer wears off.  The box in the HUD for that item will be greyed out.  Weapon buffs, like Charcoal Pine Resin, still work, though.<br />
<br />
If you are cursed for real... well, you will know if that happens lol
